{{Quote|''This is a world of airships moving over a sea of clouds. Default weather conditions change daily. Please enjoy comfortable air travel.''<br><small>(World description translated, using DeepL.)</small>}}

'''Floating Airship''' is a cross-platform cozy world. The world is set on an airship, consisting of a lobby and 2 rooms.

==Rooms==
The rooms are located on the left and right sides when spawning. Each room features the same layout but mirrored.

===Modifiers===
The rooms have 2 modifiers that users can change. The "Weather Changer" and the "Theme Changer".

